  "title": "Reader Enhancements: Share Sheet, Selectable Text, and Comments Link",
  "agent_type": "planner",
  "description": "Adds three improvements to the article reader: a native iOS share sheet (title + URL) via ShareLink in both reader toolbars, selectable/copyable body and summary text via .textSelection(.enabled), and a dormant comments-link toolbar action that activates automatically when the backend begins returning comments_url. The Article model is extended with commentsURL decoded defensively, and new unit tests cover the decoding path.",
